author: Sophie Haslett For Daily Mail Australia
title: Princess Mary wears sixties style collar awards ceremony | Daily Mail Online
text: Tried and tested! Princess Mary steps out with Sixties-style Peter Pan collar for awards ceremony... and gives favourite purple outfit a second outing Princess Mary has been busy at a business conference and awards ceremony For the conference, she sported a purple two-piece outfit worn previously The 45-year-old paired this outfit with her Joseph coat and Prada heels The Australian-born Royal later wore a Peter Pan collar at an awards ceremony The Princess and her family recently visited the Swiss Alps for a skiing holiday Published: 01:37 GMT, 24 February 2017 | Updated: 01:37 GMT, 24 February 2017 419 shares
